application_type_full: Outline planning permission: Some matters reserved
description:
Outline planning permission for the redevelopment of the
above site to provide, 24,220 m2 of Class B1 floorspace,
2,125m2 of Class B8 floorspace and 6,560 m2of residential
floor space (Class C3) in two separate buildings - one 6
storey building containing the residential accommodation and
a larger building comprising of a basement, lower ground
plus 5 storeys to the front and 6 storeys to the back with
the provision of 18 car-parking spaces within the basement
area plus parking provision for servicing,
as shown on drawing numbers 4149/001-16.
